y: it improves accuracy by aligning encoder semantics with generative context, and provides interpretable traces of how and when the decoder 'rethinks' earlier perceptions. This framework bridges cognitive models of perception with deep learning, offering a new paradigm for introspective, self-correcting Transformers.",
