ic explanations of the model's reasoning trajectory, offering unprecedented insight into how intermediate encoder knowledge is accessed and combined. We expect RAFS to significantly outperform existing models in long-context generation tasks such as abstractive summarization, dialogue response generation, and code translation, where adaptive integration of multi-granularity context is essential. Moreover, the explicit recursive structure provides a new axis for model interpretability and analysis.",
